trans-unit.target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_000<tab>Come, Dawon! We've a spot of game that wants for hunting.
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_050<tab>Dawon was...defeated? So they've bark <var 1A 02 /var>and<var 1A 01 /var> bite, then.
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC1_00000_RIAN_000_051<tab>Perhaps I'll take your measure another time. Until we meet again.
